data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Lovely, updated 3 bed, 2 bath 1950s house in quiet neighborhood near Bush Park, great schools and amenities! Wood floors, shiplap wall in dining nook and butcher board counters in kitchen. French doors lead to Trex Deck with large dog kennel below and new fence in the backyard. Finished attic for added space and finished basement with 3rd bedroom, den, and family room with access to backyard. Plum, Persimmon, Pear and Apple trees on the property with raspberry starters, strawberry and blueberry bushes.
